high_descs: Go forward to the tub, then turn right to go to the dresser.
Pick up the bar of soap from the dresser.
Turn left to face the sink.
Wash the bar of soap in the sink.
Turn around and move forward, then turn right to go to the trash can ahead.
Put the bar of soap in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean bar of soap in the trash.

high_descs: Walk forward to the tub then turn right and walk to the small white table with a box of tissues on it that's in front of you slightly to your left.
Pick up the bar of soap that's in front of you to the right of the tissues.
Turn left to face the sink.
Get the soap wet in the sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Turn around and walk past the tub then turn right and walk to the garbage that's to the right of the toilet in front of you.
Put the soap in the garbage.
anns.task_desc: Put a wet bar of soap in the garbage.

high_descs: Walk forward then turn to the right at the tub.  Turn right again and face the white counter.
Pick up a bar of soap from the counter.
Turn to the left and place the bar of soap in the sink.
Turn on the water. Then turn off the water and take out the bar of soap.
Turn around completely and turn right and go to the trash can.
Place the soap in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Wet and put a bar of soap in a trash can.
